entity-facade-xml.moqui.resource.DbResourceFile:
This server provides access to GrowERP (Moqui backend) through MCP. For ${focus?.capitalize() ?: 'General'} operations:
${focus == 'catalog' ? ''' ## Catalog Operations - Search for catalog services: `moqui_search_services(query="product")` or `query="category"` - Product prices, features and assets are managed via the growerp CatalogServices ''' : ''}
${focus == 'orders' ? ''' ## Order Operations - Orders, invoices, shipments, payments and transactions are all "financial documents": list them with `growerp.100.FinDocServices100.get#FinDoc` (set docType e.g. 'order' and sales=true/false) ''' : ''}
${focus == 'customers' ? ''' ## Customer Operations - Search for party services: `moqui_search_services(query="user")` or `query="company"` ''' : ''}
${detailLevel == 'advanced' ? ''' ## Advanced Features - Inspect raw data read-only with `moqui_rest_call` (e1/{Entity}, s1/moqui, s1/mantle) - Fetch step-by-step workflow guides with `moqui_get_help(uri="wiki:workflow:Order-Entry")` - Search company documents with `searchKnowledge`; navigate the data model with `okf_index` ''' : ''}
Use following discovery tools to explore available functionality: - `moqui_search_services`: Find growerp.* services by keyword - `moqui_get_service_details`: Get input/output parameters for a service - `moqui_execute_service`: Run a growerp.* service
